Open to any age!
Parents and kids under 4 are free with 1 paid child admission! We will take walk in admission as well on Sept 3rd! Kids under 5 need a parent supervision at all times.
pageContext.course_type_long_description: Did you know that September 3rd is officially known as National Skyscraper Day? Well, it is! Join Play-Well TEKnologies to celebrate this day by helping us build the city of Seattle out of LEGO®!  The city of Seattle has 40 Buildings over 400ft tall and has the 29th tallest building in the USA, The Columbia Center at 937 ft tall!
pageContext.course_type_name: Celebrate National Skyscraper Day with LEGO® Materials
